N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 163.5 - Quality control

State Regulations

The authorized trademark label or trademark imprint on
packages or containers shall not be used unless the farm products to be so
labeled shall have been examined by representatives duly authorized by the
department and found to meet trademark standards established for said product
by the department. Notes
